name: QuadGrip™ Cutting Board with Smart Check™ Visual Indicator

description.html:
QuadGrip with Smart Check Cutting Boards help ensure a safe cutting
surface with an integrated visual indicator, alerting operators when
it's time to replace a cutting board. When it's time to switch, the
contrasting Smart Check color between the double-sided surface shows
through. This prevents use of unsafe cutting boards with grooves and
cuts too deep to thoroughly clean in a conventional dishwasher.
QuadGrip's two-piece system with integrated Smart Check make replacing
boards cost effective and simple.

Features / Benefits

  • Integrated Smart Check Visual Indicator for replacement monitoring
  • Refillable, double-sided cutting board to reduce waste and cut costs
  • Double food safety hooks for sanitary transport and storage
  • Non-slip, reusable frame to securely hold board in place
  • Constructed of a durable co-polymer, will not warp and gentle on knives
  • Available in HACCP color-coding colors to minimize cross-contamination
  • Customize here with laser marked logos, diagrams, artwork and more
  • Refill Pack of 2 Boards

EZ–Chill™ Garnish Centers keep garnishes chilled for extended periods
of time. Designed for use with our refreezable EZ-Chill™ Ice Packs,
these centers feature ice liners that also allow for use with ice.
Full–size hinged lids will not rust and protect garnishes from spills
and contaminants. Durable stainless steel construction built to last.
Interchangeable pint and quart trays allow you to easily change
configuration as needed. EZ-Chill™ Ultimate Garnish Center (B6766L)
features two tiers (12 trays) to hold garnishes and comes complete with
two side caddies to hold straws, stirrers and picks.

Features / Benefits

  • Chill-able garnish centers; works with ice or our EZ-Chill™ ice packs (B6180)
  • Attractive and durable 22 gauge stainless steel construction
  • Hinged, transparent lids allow for easy viewing of garnishes and will not rust
  • Interchangeable pint and quart inserts
  • Includes EZ-Chill™ Refreezable Ice Packs
